text: Cassandra Lynn Scerbo (or Cassie Scerbo; March 30, 1990) is an American singer and actress. Scerbo was born in Long Island, New York. She grew up in Parkland, Florida. She has performed in several movies. She acted as Lauren in Make It or Break It.
